.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">旺區兼狗竇前面搶犯？？？就算俾你搶到，去得邊呀仆街？？？！！！</span></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>為左殤台個牌為左碗飯，童星老監馮生都要做奶共狗鳥！！！<br />\n<br />\n為紀念燒死林彬而起嘅18樓C座，狗馮既係老監亦負責主要角色，啱啱居然勁做維撚狗，幫狗政Spin話831死人只係街邊八婆鳩吹出黎，又吹香港咁大城市死幾個人點會遮得到！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘩嘩嘩！！我愈聽愈以為轉左俾Mei西監製添！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>疑點1: </ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n光明正大點解要cap圖唔直接放片？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點2: </strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解Cap既所有圖都唔見畜聾打人，直播又會見到？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點3: </strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁撚簡單既事點解要封站兩日？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點4: </strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n連721都唔會4個部門一齊見記者，點解831會？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我依家信太子有無辜市民被殺害了</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一句到尾啦，係支共命令&quot;止暴制亂&quot;之下，明知一日拖一日尤其頭七都唔交出足本只會愈拖愈亂，咁都唔交你地話點解呢？？？？</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加埋依家毛EE爆料，831事件冇人死？？？<br />\n<br />\n<strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFYI，當晚現場傳第一消息：有人打死人，但唔係香港警察，你話係邊個呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？？！！！</span></span></span></strong></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"89c03b09b3f8ee22607746f35b263401d916b56a","tid":1563224,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f7c3635de292cfbdd1e2f2b12da89974ae2914","tid":1563224,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f300bb887f3e1da89514185c826d34e0f2180679","tid":1563224,"uid":8858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:44:00.000Z","msg":"即磅即磅唔好兩頭望<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07842afc8eb1fb4628553a1db258a168de6573e","tid":1563224,"uid":81968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:44:52.000Z","msg":"出糧最撚緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb758b85fcec23ab7982dd06f5b3eb7c4b2a1206","tid":1563224,"uid":162293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:47:16.000Z","msg":"721831